AwardBIOS Part Number: 2A5IHN0A
Manufacturer: Nexcom
Core Chipset: SiS 5571
Super I/O: SMC37C669 (Check this first!!)
Award Modular BIOS v4.51PG
Unicore BIOS Upgrade Rel 2.2
